description:
A two-year-old girl arrived at the Southern Border by herself, claiming she intended to meet up with her parents, and it’s unclear why there is no national backlash regarding the government's blatant disregard for such a vulnerable child’s safety.

WATCH: An unaccompanied two-year-old child from El Salvador explains she arrived in the US by herself and that her parents are in the US. The child had a piece of paper with a phone number & name.

This morning, @TxDPS encountered a group of 211 illegal immigrants in Maverick… pic.twitter.com/rXFoqee3Kk
— Chris Olivarez (@LtChrisOlivarez) November 24, 2024
title: Watch: Unaccompanied Two-Year-Old Girl Arrives At Border With Nothing But A Note In Hand
